title: A-ha - Live in South America + bonus [1993] DVD5
description: A-ha - Live in South America + bonus [1993] On their record-breaking tour of South America a-ha played to over three million fans. The twenty-five shows took them trough Chile, Argentina and Brazil, and in Rio they broke the attendance record at Maracana Stadium with an audience of 195.000. Live in South America is a document of that tour, and captures the energy and excitement of the sold-out shows with the great performances included here. Right from start with 'The Sun Always Shines On TV' to the end with 'Take On Me' this is a rocky experience. The track listing is perfect; 'The Sun Always Shines On TV' is a perfect starter with it's exciting beginning. The highlights are 'The Sun Always...', 'Cry Wolf', 'Touchy!', 'Early Morning' and of course the perfect ending with 'Take On Me'. The concert was released in 1993 on videocassettes (VHS) and laser disc (LD - only in Japan). This DVD is not official. Ripped from laserdisk. As a bonus, 3 clips of the period Memorial Beach (1993-94) are added. Menus and chapters are present.
